217  echo "# helm_git-repo" >> README.md
  218  git init
  219  pwd
###before you package the application you need to check the path
  221  helm package /root/linux-amd64/charts/my-helm
  222  ls
  223  helm repo index .
  224  ls
  225  cat index.yaml
  226  git config --global user.email "gopal1409@gmail.com"
  227  git config --global user.name "gopal das"
  228  git add .
  229  git commit -m "my-repo"
  230  git remote add origin https://github.com/cloudarchgopal/helm_git-repo.git
  231  git branch
How to add the git helm repo to your localmachine
  236  helm repo add --username gitlogin@gmail.com --password putyourgithubtoken my-github-helm-=repo 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cloudarchgopal/helm_git-repo/master'
  237  helm repo list
